commit.message:
Fix lto report names

Some of the hash tables in lto-report are misnamed in the report.
Fix this up.

gcc/:

2013-04-22  Andi Kleen  <ak@linux.intel.com>

	* lto/lto.c (print_lto_report_1): Fix LTO report names.
